---
// Sekcja "Dla kogo jest Medykalni"
---

<section id="szkolenia" class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Dla kogo jest Medykalni
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Kafelek 1: Położne - kurs -->
      <div class="bg-background-lighter rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 group">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-accent/20 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Położne
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Kompleksowy kurs "Prowadzenie ciąży przez położną" – od diagnozy do porodu
        </p>
        <a
          href="/szkolenia/prowadzenie-ciazy-przez-polozna"
          class="block bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-dark transition-colors font-semibold text-center shadow-md hover:shadow-lg"
        >
          Zobacz kurs
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Kafelek 2: Położna na swoim - projekt -->
      <div class="bg-background-lighter rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 group">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Położna na swoim
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Program wsparcia dla położnych prowadzących własną praktykę
        </p>
        <a
          href="/projekty/polozna-na-swoim"
          class="block bg-accent text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-light transition-colors font-semibold text-center shadow-md hover:shadow-lg"
        >
          Zobacz program
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Kafelek 3: Placówki medyczne - rekrutacja -->
      <div class="bg-background-lighter rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 group">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-accent/20 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2-2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Placówki medyczne
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Kompleksowa pomoc rekrutacyjna dla klinik, gabinetów i szpitali
        </p>
        <a
          href="/dla-placowek/rekrutacja"
          class="block bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-dark transition-colors font-semibold text-center shadow-md hover:shadow-lg"
        >
          Zobacz ofertę
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
